headline: Empower Appoints Sangita Woerner as Chief Marketing Officer
summary: GREENWOOD VILLAGE, Colo., September 23, 2025--Empower, a leading provider of retirement services and wealth management, is today announcing the appointment of Sangita Woerner as its new Chief Marketing Officer (CMO).
